existing_features.title: Replace the existing “blue suitcase” icon with a minimal purple target/mission icon in all requested UI locations: (1) the top-left icon on the yellow page of the app, and (2) the icon shown in the welcome intro/onboarding screen. Implement the icon using the existing missions purple theme (e.g., Tailwind `text-missions-accent`) so it reads as a mission-related app element.

new_feature_requests.summary: Replace the blue suitcase icon (top-left on the yellow page and in the welcome intro) with a minimal purple target/mission icon to better convey mission creation.

projectName: Replace blue suitcase icon with minimal purple mission target icon
